    <h2>6. Chargebacks</h2>
    <p>We encourage you to contact us directly before initiating a chargeback with your bank or payment provider. We are committed to resolving all genuine disputes fairly and promptly.</p>
    <p>Fraudulent chargebacks on products that were delivered as described may result in account suspension and may be reported to relevant authorities.</p>

    <h2>7. Exchanges</h2>
    <p>In some cases, instead of a refund, we may offer to exchange your purchase for a different product of equal or lesser value. This will be determined on a case-by-case basis.</p>

